features: 【AWAKEN YOUR GLOW WITH OVERNIGHT PEEL OFF CARE】 Protect and enhance your skin's elasticity and hydration with our collagen face mask, this collagen overnight peel-off mask delivers 24-hour nourishment while you sleep, improves skin firmness, elasticity, glow, and hydration, reduces sagging and dullness for a glowy appearance by morning.

【POWERFUL INGREDIENTS】 Powered by Hydrolyzed Collagen, Ceramide EOS and Tocopherol, this collagen night wrapping mask enhances skin elasticity and delivers a radiant, glass skin glow. Ceramide EOS for skin barrier and hydration, Hydrolyzed Collagen for elasticity hydration and youthful complexion, Tocopherol for reducing fine lines. These powerful ingredients of this collagen mask works synergistically to brighten and strengthen the skin barrier, promoting radiant, youthful skin.

【IMPROVE SKIN ELASTICITY】 The overnight face mask provides intensive moisture while tightening skin. Enriched with hydrolyzed collagen, this peel off face masks can penetrate deeply into skin to strengthen elasticity, reduces skin sagging and fine lines, helping to boost skin elasticity for a firmer, more youthful complexion overnight.

【ENHANCE HYDRATION & RADIANCE】 Infused with Collagen for deep hydration, this korean face mask locks in moisture while improving skin firmness, creates a breathable protective barrier that effectively locks in moisture, ensuring continuous hydration throughout the night, leaving your skin more hydrated, radiant, and visibly glowing by morning.

【15 MINS COLLAGEN BOOST PEEF OFF MASK】 This face masks skincare is designed to hydrate and tighten your skin. Achieve visibly firmer, plumper skin in just 15 minutes with our collagen night mask skin care. This peel off mask comes with a silicone brush for a smooth application. Simply apply an even layer, let it work overnight, and gently peel off or rinse in the morning.
